<template>
    <v-app>
      <template v-if="accessToken != null && proceed">
        <Navbar/>
        <v-container style="width: 1012px; height: 100%" class="teal lighten-5">
            <router-view
              :key="$route.fullPath"
              />
          </v-container>
        </template>
        <template v-else-if="proceed">
          <router-view
            :key="$route.fullPath"
            />
        </template>
    </v-app>
</template>

<script type="text/javascript">
import Navbar from "@/components/Navbar.vue"
import { mapGetters } from "vuex";
import {
  USER_FETCH,
} from "@/store/actions.type";

  export default {
    name: "App",
    data() {
      return {
        proceed: false,
      }
    },
    components: {
      Navbar
    },
    computed: {
      ...mapGetters(["activeUser", "accessToken"]),
    },
    watch: {
      activeUser () {
        this.setUserInfo();
      },
    },
    methods: {
      setUserInfo() {
        if (this._.isEmpty(this.activeUser)) {
          this.$store.dispatch(USER_FETCH)
        }
      },
    },
    // created() {
    //   this.setUserInfo();
    // },
    mounted() {
      if (this.accessToken === null) {
        this.proceed = true;
        this.$router.push({ name: 'login' });
      } else {
        this.proceed = true;
        this.setUserInfo();
      }
    }
  }
</script>
